  </div>

  <div class="eyebrow">Panic never wins</div>
  <h1 class="headline">Every other app<br><strong>manages</strong> panic.<br>Waypoint <strong>proves</strong> you survive it.</h1>
  <p class="sub">A calm, guided protocol for the moment panic hits — and a growing record of every time you got through it. Not therapy. Not a diagnosis. Just evidence.</p>

