</header>

<section class="alt">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2 class="display">Your evidence builds.</h2>
    <p>Every attack you survive gets logged. Not as a symptom. As proof. Over weeks and months, that record becomes a quiet, undeniable argument against the fear that says "this time will be different."</p>
  </div>
  <div class="evidence-demo">
    <div class="evidence-card">
      <div class="evidence-number">14</div>
      <div class="evidence-label">Attacks survived</div>
      <div class="evidence-quote">"Every attack so far has ended."</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2 class="display">One button. That's it.</h2>
    <p>When it hits, you don't have to think or decide anything. Waypoint walks you through it, one calm step at a time.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>You are safe</h3>
        <p>A slow countdown gives your body a moment to land, with nothing to figure out.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>One slow breath</h3>
        <p>A quick check-in on whether you can breathe with the app right now — no wrong answer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Breathe together</h3>
        <p>A guided breathing pattern, paced with gentle haptics, until your body starts to settle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Ground yourself</h3>
        <p>The 5-4-3-2-1 technique, one sense at a time, to bring you back into the room.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">5</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>The wave passes</h3>
        <p>A moment to recognize what just happened — and that you stayed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">6</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>It becomes evidence</h3>
        <p>Logged, counted, and added to the growing case that you get through this.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="crisis-strip">
  <div class="wrap crisis-strip-inner">
